<collectingCountry id="32CB7663FFFBFFBAFE7599376B1078EA" box="[479,541,1395,1419]" name="Libya" pageId="22" pageNumber="36">Libya</collectingCountry>
by BERGGREN &amp; AUBERT (1975). Also, it is recorded by LUGER (1985) in the Paleocene (Garra Formation). It is recorded in the Esna Shale of the Esh El Mallaha area.
</paragraph>
